Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,WEATHERVANE — finds the weather window before the planner finishes\Ntheir coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM challenge: contested logistics + expeditionary operations need\Nreal-time environmental intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fusing NASA MERRA-2, GPM IMERG, MODIS, GHRSST and WAVEWATCH III — no\Ndata movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Planner asks: amphibious landing at Subic Bay, 14–21 May. WEATHERVANE\Nanswers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamiwaza-deployed model fuses five timeseries into a typed go/no-go\Ngrade and a 4-hour H-hour window.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Five charts render with the recommended window highlighted in green.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:01:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrative brief — planner-grade prose, source-cited, ready for the\NOPORD annex.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL=https://kamiwaza.local/api/v1 and the same code\Nstays inside the wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
